<link title="Javier Fernandez Garcia-Boente"><link title="Javier Fernandez Garcia-Boente"><p>Test passes if there is a <strong>filled green square</strong> and <strong>no red</strong>.</p>
<link rel="help" title="4.1.0. Phase II: Trimming and Positioning" href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-text-3/#white-space-phase-2"><meta name="assert" charset="utf-8">
<link rel="help" href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-text-3/#valdef-white-space-normal"><link rel="help" href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-text-3/#valdef-white-space-normal"><link rel="help" href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-text-3/#valdef-white-space-normal"><link rel="help" href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-text-3/#valdef-white-space-normal">
